description: A list of all the concrete types defined in this version of the FHIR specification - Abstract Types, Data Types and Resource Types.

extension.valueString: This Value Set is normative - it is generated based on the information defined in this specification. The definition will remain fixed  across versions, but the actual contents will change from version to version

name: FHIRAllTypes

text.div:
This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/data-types
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/resource-types
  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/abstract-types

title: FHIRAllTypes
